<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 06:17:18 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>所罗门群岛告诉澳大利亚它仍然是首选合作伙伴</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/solomon-islands-tells-australia-it-remains-partner-choice-2024-05-21/</link><description>所罗门群岛新当选总理杰里米亚·马内莱表示，随着澳大利亚副总理理查德·马勒斯周二访问澳大利亚，这个太平洋岛国已准备好与澳大利亚讨论“更广泛的双边合作”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 04:40:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/solomon-islands-tells-australia-it-remains-partner-choice-2024-05-21/</guid></item><item><title>韩国任命另一位世界杯预选赛临时教练</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/south-korea-appoint-another-interim-coach-world-cup-qualifiers-2024-05-21/</link><description>由于韩国足协（KFA）未能及时任命常任教练来接替尤尔根·克林斯曼，金度勋将率领韩国队参加 6 月份对阵新加坡和中国的世界杯预选赛。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 03:46:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/south-korea-appoint-another-interim-coach-world-cup-qualifiers-2024-05-21/</guid></item><item><title>快充网络不足 理想汽车推迟纯电动SUV上市</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/li-auto-delays-pure-electric-suv-launch-due-insufficient-fast-charging-network-2024-05-21/</link><description>中国理想汽车表示，由于缺乏足够的快速充电桩等障碍，其纯电动 SUV 车型的推出计划已推迟至明年，导致其股价周二下跌逾 17%。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 03:37:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/li-auto-delays-pure-electric-suv-launch-due-insufficient-fast-charging-network-2024-05-21/</guid></item><item><title>中国驻日本大使馆表示反对日本议员访问台湾</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-embassy-japan-says-it-opposes-japanese-lawmakers-visiting-taiwan-2024-05-21/</link><description>中国驻日本大使馆周二表示，坚决反对日本议员访问台湾，并表示坚决抗议。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 03:34:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-embassy-japan-says-it-opposes-japanese-lawmakers-visiting-taiwan-2024-05-21/</guid></item><item><title>中国谴责韩国、日本议员访问台湾</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-embassy-south-korea-says-it-opposes-lawmakers-visiting-taiwan-2024-05-21/</link><description>中国周二谴责韩国和日本议员不顾中国的强烈反对而访问台湾，并指责这两个邻国参加台湾的“所谓领导人就职典礼”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 03:22:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-embassy-south-korea-says-it-opposes-lawmakers-visiting-taiwan-2024-05-21/</guid></item><item><title>随着美联储焦点的加强，股市下滑，美元坚挺；加密货币飙升</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-05-21/</link><description>周二，亚洲股市走低，而美元坚挺，因投资者等待美联储最新政策会议纪要，以评估今年可能降息的时机和程度。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 03:01:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-05-21/</guid></item><item><title>美元稳定；以太币引发加密货币反弹</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-steady-ether-fuels-crypto-rally-2024-05-21/</link><description>周二美元坚挺，而日元则在 156 水平的弱侧挣扎，但交易大多区间波动，因为投资者普遍坚持对美联储今年降息的预期时间和幅度的看法。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 00:53:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-steady-ether-fuels-crypto-rally-2024-05-21/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：亚洲股市有望创 2021 年以来最佳表现</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-05-20/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 21:48:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-05-20/</guid></item><item><title>贝莱德举报人因解雇、关闭中国监控工具而提起诉讼</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/blackrock-whistleblower-alleges-cover-up-search-engine-spot-chinese-investments-2024-05-20/</link><description>贝莱德被一位举报的前副总裁起诉，索赔 2000 万美元，他表示，在他反对同事的自我交易后，贝莱德解雇了他，并被迫关闭了一个用于监控客户有关非法投资（包括在中国）讨论的搜索引擎。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 16:42:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/legal/blackrock-whistleblower-alleges-cover-up-search-engine-spot-chinese-investments-2024-05-20/</guid></item><item><title>参议院报告称，宝马向美国进口了 8,000 辆汽车，其零部件来自被禁止的中国供应商</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/bmw-imported-8000-vehicles-into-us-with-parts-banned-chinese-supplier-senate-2024-05-20/</link><description>美国参议院周一发布的一份报告称，德国汽车制造商宝马向美国进口了至少 8,000 辆 Mini Cooper 汽车，其电子元件来自被禁止的中国供应商。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 13:30:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/bmw-imported-8000-vehicles-into-us-with-parts-banned-chinese-supplier-senate-2024-05-20/</guid></item><item><title>焦点：随着美国发货平息投机者的狂热，铜的创纪录运行面临风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/coppers-record-run-risk-us-shipments-calm-speculator-frenzy-2024-05-20/</link><description>未来几周，铜价飙升至历史新高的势头可能无法持续，行动主要集中在运送材料以弥补美国商品交易所期货市场暴露的空头头寸，而不是最大消费国中国的不温不火的需求。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 13:19:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/coppers-record-run-risk-us-shipments-calm-speculator-frenzy-2024-05-20/</guid></item><item><title>价格创历史新高时有关铜市场的主要事实</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/main-facts-about-copper-market-prices-hit-record-highs-2024-05-20/</link><description>周一，由于空头回补引发的近期反弹，为投机者和基金押注金属价格上涨创造了动力，铜价飙升至历史新高。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 12:55:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/main-facts-about-copper-market-prices-hit-record-highs-2024-05-20/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：“Nvidia 周”开局活跃</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-05-20/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 10:05:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-05-20/</guid></item><item><title>路透调查显示，中国房价暴跌，今年销售状况将恶化</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/slump-chinas-home-prices-sales-set-worsen-this-year-2024-05-20/</link><description>路透调查显示，随着房地产投资和销售下滑​​加剧，今年中国房价将以更快的速度下跌，这对正在加倍努力重振受危机打击的房地产行业的政策制定者来说是一个沉重的提醒。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 09:54:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/slump-chinas-home-prices-sales-set-worsen-this-year-2024-05-20/</guid></item><item><title>经济复苏乏力，1-4月中国财政收入下降2.7%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-fiscal-revenue-shrank-27-jan-april-amid-shaky-economic-recovery-2024-05-20/</link><description>继1月至3月下滑2.3%后，2024年前4个月中国财政收入同比下滑2.7%，进一步表明经济复苏不平衡。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 09:32:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-fiscal-revenue-shrank-27-jan-april-amid-shaky-economic-recovery-2024-05-20/</guid></item></channel></rss>